# Public catalogue (/inventory) reads listed cards live from the Card Books database.
# Both values are PUBLISHABLE (safe in a client bundle) — the card-books project's URL + anon key.
# The anon key can ONLY read the public_catalogue view (6 columns of listed Inventory cards); everything else is denied by RLS.
